rows.label: tlk70000009_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Thanks to the excellent judgment
of Squad Leader Onyx, I was promoted
to guarding the watchtower.

rows.label: tlk70000009_02_msg0002
rows.name:
What a great view! You can see the
whole city. I guess this is what they
call "moving up in the world." Haha!

rows.label: tlk70000009_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I can see the gate... And my big
brother guarding the gate. He looks
like a tiny ant down there.

rows.label: tlk70000009_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Well... What's done is done. I'm
going to do what I can to protect
Iira. And I'll do it my way, dammit!
